title: PROJECT POWER Ending Explained!
author: Think Story
comment: Would you take the 💊 if you could? What power would you want?
This movie wasn't terrible but I think would have been better as a 10 episode series. Just not enough time to develop more depth into the powers/world.
Art has the power to take life and Tracy has the power to give life
nobody’s gonna mention how Tracy could’ve healed Robins mother?!?

One thing I noticed is that when the guy was talking about animal evolution he talked about how some animals can break their bones to squeeze under tight places, and how the wolverine rat can break its bones to give it daggers. Both of these powers come up on the boat.
description:
In this video we take a deep dive, review, recap and explain the ending to Netflix's latest sci-fi superhero action movie PROJECT POWER starring Jamie Foxx, Joseph Gordon-Levitt and Dominique Fishback.
